<template>
  <router-view/>
</template>

<script>
import {router} from './router';
export default {
  name: 'App',
  created() {
    const storedToken = localStorage.getItem('token');
    if (storedToken == "") {
      router.push('/signin');
    }
  },
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
